title: Get In Loser, We're Starting a Podcast | Ep. 1
itunes:author: Yeah No I Know, Jenna, Brooklin & Kristen Leanne
description: One of us had her first child at 19, one rode a horse through a drive-thru and the other has never farted in front of her boyfriend. Hope you're prepared for our candor; embarrassing stories are not off the table. Actually, nothing is!
